Class Script.Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      • com.storytron.uber.Script.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TNode, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode
    Enclosing class:
    Script

    public static final class Script.Node
extends javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, TNode
    Nodes for scripts. They have an operator, a description, a boolean telling if they are expanded, and if the operator is a constant operator there is also the constant value.
    See Also:
